ComicInfo.Title: Whom the Gods Would Destroy!; The Summons!
ComicInfo.Summary:
Whom the Gods Would Destroy!: Thor and Hercules fight over Jane Foster. Odin, still angry because Thor revealed his identity to Jane, removes half Thor's powers by giving 'Odin Power' to Seidring. Hercules defeats Thor.
The Summons!: The Argonauts are called home to Asgard by Odin.
